Package src.controller

Class BookingManager

java.lang.Object
src.controller.BookingManager
public class BookingManager extends Object
BookingManager is a controller class that acts as a "middleman" between the view classes - CineplexAppView, MovieView, ShowtimeView and the model class - Booking
